fc1acc341b.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E5%90%83%E8%85%B0%E5%AD%90%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E5%90%83%E8%85%B0%E5%AD%90%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#经常吃腰子的人身体会有什么变化#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;猪肾（猪腰子）的硒含量丰富，100g的猪腰子就有157mg的硒，几口就能满足全天的需求。另外，猪腰子维生素B1含量也不少，是细粮的好搭档，适合孕妇、哺乳妈妈、缺铁性贫血者、主食过于精细的人。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;但和其他动物肾脏一样，它的胆固醇含量极高，如果你经常吃，“三高”也就离你不远了。&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[doge]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（科普中国）&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hph13u8w4fj20q00d0tar.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/OdbGV5Csb</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/OdbGV5Csb</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 08:25:53 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item></channel></rss>